author: Inside Edition
description: Fear is gripping the city of Providence, Rhode Island, as the Brown University gunman remains on the loose. Six local private schools have closed or switched to remote learning and four local colleges have joined Brown University in canceling classes. Police have also stepped up security at public schools in the city. Inside Edition spoke with Mayor Brett Smiley. Just released video shows the suspected gunman walking outside. The FBI put out a wanted poster with a $50,000 reward.
title: Fear Grips Providence, Rhode Island As Shooter Remains On The Loose

author: Inside Edition
description: Sydney Sweeney turned heads wearing a white dress at the Los Angeles of her new movie "The Housemaid." Sweeney's vintage vibe drew comparisons to Marilyn Monroe's gown in the movie "The Seven Year Itch." Co-star Amanda Seyfried joined Sweeney on the red carpet and posed for selfies with fans. Meanwhile, Donald Trump Jr announced that he is getting married to girlfriend Bettina Anderson. Anderso,39, says she's thrilled to join the First Family.
title: Sydney Sweeney Turns Heads At Premiere of 'The Housemaid'

author: Inside Edition
description: This may come as a surprise, but there's a good chance you are wearing the hood on your winter coat wrong. A hat trick one woman posted on social media has gone viral. Jessica Alzamora is from Chicago and posted a video on how she wears her coat. Within 24 hours of posting the video, it had more than 5 million views. Inside Edition went to the crossroads of the world, Times Square, to show how to use your hood to stay warm.
title: What Is The Right Way To Wear Your Winter Coat?

author: Inside Edition
description: Ashley Wasielewski was heading home in Georgia when a stranger walked up behind her and poured acid over her head. Wasielewski's best friend Connor Milam and son Wesley have been by her side since the attack. The 46-year-old mom of two sons was transported to a trauma center with burns over 50 percent of her body. Wasielewski may never be able to grow hair on her head again. Now, as Wasielewski struggles to heal, her family is seeking justice.
title: Man Pours Acid Over Woman In Georgia Park

author: Inside Edition
description: Former first lady Michelle Obama revealed she and former President Barack Obama were supposed to be with Rob Reiner and his wife, Michele, on the day they were murdered. Hours earlier, Rob, Michele, and their son Nick attended a holiday party at Conan O'Brien's home. According to a report, a loud argument broke out between Rob and Nick. New details are coming to light about what followed. Police arrested Nick on murder charges in downtown Los Angeles.
title: The Obamas Had Plans To See Reiners On Day Of Murders

author: Inside Edition
description: President Donald Trump is doubling down on his shocking criticism of slain director Rob Reiner. Big names who are solidly in Trump's corner are slamming his reaction to the murder of the Hollywood icon and his wife, Michele. Piers Morgan said, "That just crosses a line of basic human decency." Fox News personality Greg Gutfeld said he would have handled it differently. Laura Ingraham did not mention President Trump, but she praised Reiner.
title: President Trump Under Fire After Criticizing Rob Reiner

description: Authorities believed they had a person of interest in the Brown University shootings, but less than 24 hours later, police found that basic forensic tests showed they had the wrong person.
title: Search For Brown University Shooter Continues #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: A California family says they were the targets of an anti-Semitic attack on the first night of Hanukkah, when shots were fired outside their home. It happened in the City of Redlands, where Dr. Rodgir Cohen has a very festive holiday display set up. He tells CBS News he has noticed an increase in anti-Semitism, but didn't think it would come to his front door. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Shots Fired Outside California Home With Elaborate Hanukkah Decorations

title: Doordash Driver Charged For Allegedly Pepper Spraying Order #shorts
